{"tid":268491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小一派位】雙非家長準備好文件叩門：香港教育制度好啲","createTime":"2017-06-03T05:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T07:37:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0983343dd778a846190cdd9e37750e737d0bdb6e","tid":268491,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170603/large/1496463677_fa0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170603%2Flarge%2F1496463677_fa0b.jpg&h=cd372ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 小一統一派位結果今早出爐，雖然天氣悶然，但在北區上水的校網80，上午9時前便已有逾70名家長在統一派位中心門外等候。<br />\n<br />\n派頭位的廖女士是本地家長，今早6時已在門外等候，她稱自己早到是因爲心情緊張，並坦言對派位結果的心情猶如「等抽獎」。她又指，自己孫女的首三志願都是自己屬意的小學，所以第四志願起方會考慮叩門。<br />\n<br />\n校網80亦有非本地家長申請報讀，家長舒女士是雙非家長，她指女兒自小已在香港讀幼稚園，故也希望在香港升讀小學。她又表示，自己現時也在北區有住所，但未有明言是置業或租住。居住於上水的單非家長劉小姐則表示，自己也擔心不滿意派位成績需要叩門，但她其後又表示「順其自然」。<br />\n<br />\n另一位雙非家長莊先生排隊時已準備好文件作叩門之用，他說，自己對香港的教育制度有信心，所以希望小朋友來港讀書。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，本年度共有32,235名學童參加派位，人數創10年新高。獲派首3志願的學童共21,785人，比率為67.6%，較去年微跌約1.4個百分點，連同獲派自行分配學額的3,297人，派位整體滿意率為81.3%，與過去兩年相若。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56777061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56777061&d=Meg8eMkED75wBlDILqO4uozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=acccb9a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56777061&h=89c61b0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56777061</a>"},{"pid":"d1980d567ddaf8f74f164821dde22d12fb2c53ca","tid":268491,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"支那邊方面唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57789e6e25d85aa4713eddf3676f2ce925409d9","tid":268491,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那邊方面唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反了反了"},{"pid":"00632a631adbaaa0bab88e725ddd63f44cebf751","tid":268491,"uid":27009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"返支那讀啦屌你"},{"pid":"e6fb5bf9edb9f19a911e798a6220d5c3bd26acc5","tid":268491,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那邊方面唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那高考好撚痴線"}]}